{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d67a454026","title":"中央文革对穆欣问题的几次电话指示","origin":"周良霄、顾菊英编《疯狂、扭曲与堕落的年代》之二——《十年文革中首长讲话传信录》, 2009。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8eece18ae3","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":28,"articleId":"d67a454026"}],"tags":[{"id":"269c664f91","name":"阎长贵","type":"人物"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"57434e107b","name":"戚本禹","type":"人物"},{"id":"6767f054ce","name":"穆欣","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"9014e20fdf","name":"戚本禹"},{"id":"b012f55db3","name":"阎长贵"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"41413929fb","type":"title","text":"中央文革对穆欣问题的几次电话指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"},{"id":"3a2a7e0cb5","type":"authors","text":"陈伯达阎长贵戚本禹","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"},{"id":"a9c9b15326","type":"subtitle","text":"(1967年1月28日，电话记录稿)","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"},{"id":"a78b761c04","type":"subtitle","text":"1967年1月28日O时45分","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"},{"id":"098ee93cc4","type":"paragraph","text":"中央文革小组办公室韩树信给清华赵雪林同学的电话：","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"},{"id":"f0c3d11dd0","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达同志的电话记录不要印，未经审查即发，伯达同志不同意。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"},{"id":"3284515b1d","type":"paragraph","text":"穆欣的问题，可以揭发、批判。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"},{"id":"014aa23f38","type":"subtitle","text":"1967年1月28日4时多","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"},{"id":"8c46779106","type":"paragraph","text":"阎长贵同志电话，由罗杰接","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"},{"id":"77744b8517","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达同志口授：这个讲话不要发，不管是否属实，都不要发。谁发谁负责。伯达同志打电话，是和来电话的同志交换意见，不能开把电话交换意见就印成传单这种先例。这样做以后就不好说话了。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"},{"id":"b8a7c37d22","type":"subtitle","text":"1967年1月28日中午12点10分","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"},{"id":"108891ae02","type":"paragraph","text":"中央文革办公室电话：","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"},{"id":"bc5514f90b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志委托办公室同志，关于伯达同志对穆欣问题答复如下：","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"},{"id":"8461382391","type":"appellation","text":"你们寄来的材料，伯达同志已经看到了。穆欣可以揭发、批判，而且应该彻底揭发、批判。伯达同志并不保谁。他只是说穆欣性质现在暂时不要定，以后待揭发事实后再定。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"},{"id":"1da3de7ef6","type":"paragraph","text":"电话记录不能印发，因为没有经过他本人审阅。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026"}],"page":{"id":"9af19c36d9","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d67a454026","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}